These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, amaryllis, poppy
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the person who growsdahlia##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Flower      | amaryllis  | dahlia | poppy        | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, manager, coach, doctor
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the coach##7
2. the doctor is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5
3. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the manager is on the left of the doctor##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Job     | coach | manager       | doctor         | accountant     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

