.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, malaysian, german, thai
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the thai##1
2. the thai is somewhere between the malaysian and the mexican##7
3. the german is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the mexican is somewhere between the thai and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Nationality   | german | mexican  | thai   | malaysian |

