.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, purple, pink, amber
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes coral is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the person who likes amber##7
3. the person who likes pink is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Color   | purple | coral | amber       | pink |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

