.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, snake, chinchilla
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the german is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the owner of the rabbit##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | snake | rabbit   | chinchilla | frog |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

