.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, van, bike
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
6. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the taxi##7
7. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | bike | taxi   | van |

