1. the argentine is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the far left or far right##3
4. the spanish is somewhere between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsbellflower##7
5. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Flower          | tulip    | daffodil   | begonia | bellflower  |
| Nationality   | argentine | nigerian | spanish    | chinese |

