.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, biathlon, rowing, water-polo
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rabbit
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Sport   | water-polo | rowing | biathlon | weightlifting |
| Pet           | horse   | rabbit    | dog       | hamster  |

