.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, august, october, july
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, r&b, techno
1. the person who's birthday is in december is not the fan of classical##6
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person who's birthday is in august##7
6. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Birthday           | july | december | october | august |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | r&b      | classical | pop            |

