.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, airplane, tram, van
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, rat, snake
1. the person driving the van is somewhere between the person driving the car and the owner of the snake##7
2. the person driving the airplane is not the owner of the rat##6
3. the owner of the mouse is not the person driving the tram##6
4. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the person driving the car is the owner of the dog##1
6. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Transport   | car | van | airplane | tram |
| Pet           | dog    | mouse   | snake  | rat      |

