The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, rock, soul, trance
1. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
4. the australian is on the left of the italian##1
5. the italian is between the malaysian and the fan of rock##2
6. the fan of soul is somewhere between the fan of rock and the malaysian##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | australian | italian | malaysian | indian   |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | soul      | gospel      | trance |

