.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, brazilian, malaysian, dutch
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, subway, trike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the dutch is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the subway is the malaysian##1
4. the malaysian is not the person driving the bus##6
5. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the malaysian##7
7. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
