.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, cain, tiparillo, blend
1. the cain-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the blend-smoker is somewhere between the person drinking water and the tiparillo-smoker##7
3. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
4. the tiparillo-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | cola   | mirinda | fanta | water   |
| Cigar   | havana | tiparillo   | blend | cain |

