.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, skydiving, sudoku
There 4 different types of food: radish, asparagus, apple, plum
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person eating plum##7
2. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person eating asparagus##5
3. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person eating plum##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person eating radish and the person eating apple##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | sudoku     | drawing     | rock-climbing |
| Food     | plum | apple | asparagus | radish     |

