.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, december, october
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, reggae, salsa, techno
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the fan of metal##7
5. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the person who's birthday is in february##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Birthday           | february | october | december | january  |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | reggae   | salsa    | techno |

