4. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
