3. the person playing monopoly is not the person watching documentary movies##6
4. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
5. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person playing monopoly##7
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Game           | monopoly | canasta  | backgammon  | billiard |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | horror | documentary | drama   |

