2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
4. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the trike is not the person drinking mirinda##6
6. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking mirinda##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage   | tea | mirinda | 7up      | coffee |
| Transport     | trike  | skateboard  | motorbike | boat   |

