.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, teacher, coach, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, scooter
1. the coach is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the teacher##7
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the pilot is on the left of the musician##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
5. the coach is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Job         | teacher    | coach | pilot     | musician |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

 